id: pm-zdec
title: Add dependency mutation command for existing items
description: Metadata audit found 102 items with empty dependencies and no supported CLI mutation path to add dependency links after item creation.
type: Issue
status: open
priority: 1
tags[5]: "area:dependencies","area:metadata",core,pm-cli,release-readiness
