estimated_minutes: 180
acceptance_criteria: "A supported CLI path can add and remove dependency entries on existing items with history tracking, ownership semantics, and regression tests, enabling closure of dependency metadata gaps across all items."
definition_of_ready: Dependency schema and ownership semantics are validated against current item format and history rules.
order: 1
goal: metadata-completeness
objective: enable-post-create-dependency-mutations
value: unblocks-full-item-completeness-audits
impact: removes-manual-gaps-in-dependency-linking
