severity: medium
environment: linux-node25-local
repro_steps: 1) Run pm list-all --json and identify items with empty dependencies 2) Attempt pm update --dep ... 3) Observe unknown option and no alternative dependency mutation command
resolution: implement a dedicated dependency mutation surface for existing items
expected_result: Agents can add dependency entries to existing items via a supported command and history records capture each mutation.
actual_result: Dependency links can be seeded at create-time but cannot be mutated on existing items through current CLI commands.
